    "body" : "<p>The HttpServletRequest object provides a map of parameters already. See <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/cd/E17802_01/products/products/servlet/2.3/javadoc/javax/servlet/ServletRequest.html#getParameterMap()\" rel=\"noreferrer\">request.getParameterMap()</a> for more details.</p>\n"
