    "answer_id" : 9070197,
    "question_id" : 7312436,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <code>org.springframework.web.context.request.WebRequest</code> as a parameter in your controller method, it provides the method <code>getParameterMap()</code>, the advantage is that you do not tight your application to the Servlet API, the WebRequest is a example of JavaEE pattern Context Object.</p>\n"
