    "question_id" : 7312436,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I might be late to the party,\nbut as per my understanding , you're looking for something like this :</p>\n\n<pre><code>for(String params : Collections.list(httpServletRequest.getParameterNames())) {\n    // Whatever you want to do with your map\n    // Key : params\n    // Value : httpServletRequest.getParameter(params)                \n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 5648860,
      "reputation" : 9905,
      "user_id" : 4470135,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 54,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/oXA6y.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "yuranos",
