    "creation_date" : 1539005081,
    "answer_id" : 52703357,
    "question_id" : 7312436,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>@SuppressWarnings(\"unchecked\")\nMap&lt;String,String[]&gt; requestMapper=request.getParameterMap();\nJsonObject jsonObject=new JsonObject();\nfor(String key:requestMapper.keySet()){\n    jsonObject.addProperty(key, requestMapper.get(key)[0]);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>All params will be stored in <code>jsonObject</code>.</p>\n"
  } ],
